{
  "title": "Crunchy Tangy Tunisian Chickpeas Salad",
  "description": "A zesty, crunchy salad bursting with Tunisian flavors, sweet peppadew peppers, and a quick harissa‑lemon dressing—ideal for a comforting sick‑day meal.",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
